                <h2 class="section-title" data-lang-ja="3. Destin Power社 PCS" data-lang-en="3. Destin Power PCS">3. Destin Power社 PCS</h2>
                <p class="mb-4" data-lang-ja="Destin Power社は、特に<strong class='font-semibold'>ESS用PCS</strong>に注力しており、持続可能なエネルギー革新を目指しています。" data-lang-en="Destin Power focuses particularly on <strong class='font-semibold'>PCS for ESS</strong>, aiming for sustainable energy innovation.">Destin Power社は、特に<strong class='font-semibold'>ESS用PCS</strong>に注力しており、持続可能なエネルギー革新を目指しています。</p>
                <div>
                    <button class="accordion-button">
                        <span data-lang-ja="3.1. 主な特徴" data-lang-en="3.1. Main Features">3.1. 主な特徴</span>
                        <span class="arrow">&#9654;</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content p-4 bg-white border border-t-0 rounded-b-md">
                        <h3 class="sub-section-title" data-lang-ja="液浸冷却技術" data-lang-en="Immersion Cooling Technology"><strong class="font-semibold">液浸冷却技術</strong>
                            <button class="term-explain-button" data-term-ja="液浸冷却" data-term-en="Immersion Cooling">✨<span data-lang-key="explain_term_button" data-lang-ja="解説" data-lang-en="Explain">解説</span></button>
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mb-2">
                            <li data-lang-ja="特に<strong class='font-semibold'>高容量ESS用PCS</strong>で<strong class='font-semibold'>液浸冷却</strong>を採用。" data-lang-en="Employs <strong class='font-semibold'>immersion cooling</strong>, especially for <strong class='font-semibold'>high-capacity ESS PCS</strong>.">特に<strong class='font-semibold'>高容量ESS用PCS</strong>で<strong class='font-semibold'>液浸冷却</strong>を採用。</li>
                            <li data-lang-ja="冷却システム：PEBB TANK（IGBT格納部）、REACTOR TANKをCDUからのクーラントで直接冷却。熱交換器で外部冷却源（チラー等）へ熱を伝達。" data-lang-en="Cooling system: PEBB TANK (IGBT housing) and REACTOR TANK are directly cooled by coolant from a CDU. Heat is transferred to an external cooling source (chiller, etc.) via a heat exchanger.">冷却システム：PEBB TANK（IGBT格納部）、REACTOR TANKをCDUからのクーラントで直接冷却。熱交換器で外部冷却源（チラー等）へ熱を伝達。</li>
                        </ul>
                         <div class="conversation-info">
                            <p data-lang-ja="[会話情報] IGBT基盤とリアクトルを別々のケースに入れ、<strong class='font-semibold'>絶縁性オイルを充填</strong>して冷却（<strong class='font-semibold'>オイルシーリング</strong>）。これによりPCS筐体は<strong class='font-semibold'>IP65以上</strong>の高防塵防水性能を確保。" data-lang-en="[Conversation Info] IGBT board and reactor are placed in separate cases and cooled by <strong class='font-semibold'>filling with insulating oil</strong> (<strong class='font-semibold'>oil sealing</strong>). This ensures high dust/water proofing (<strong class='font-semibold'>IP65+</strong>) for the PCS enclosure."><strong>[会話情報]</strong> IGBT基盤とリアクトルを別々のケースに入れ、<strong class='font-semibold'>絶縁性オイルを充填</strong>して冷却（<strong class='font-semibold'>オイルシーリング</strong>）。これによりPCS筐体は<strong class='font-semibold'>IP65以上</strong>の高防塵防水性能を確保。</p>
                            <p data-lang-ja="[会話情報] 外部水源（海水・淡水）利用の<strong class='font-semibold'>プレート型熱交換器</strong>を採用。冷却回路は<strong class='font-semibold'>分離設計</strong>（外部水と機器冷却水は非接触）。" data-lang-en="[Conversation Info] Employs <strong class='font-semibold'>plate heat exchangers</strong> using external water sources (seawater/freshwater). The cooling circuit is a <strong class='font-semibold'>separate design</strong> (external water and equipment coolant do not directly contact)."><strong>[会話情報]</strong> 外部水源（海水・淡水）利用の<strong class='font-semibold'>プレート型熱交換器</strong>を採用。冷却回路は<strong class='font-semibold'>分離設計</strong>（外部水と機器冷却水は非接触）。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                    <button class="accordion-button">
                        <span data-lang-ja="3.2. 製品情報 (SAVEENシリーズ)" data-lang-en="3.2. Product Information (SAVEEN Series)">3.2. 製品情報 (SAVEENシリーズ)</span>
                        <span class="arrow">&#9654;</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content p-4 bg-white border border-t-0 rounded-b-md">
                        <p data-lang-ja="製品名: ESS用PCS「<strong class='font-semibold'>SAVEEN</strong>」。液浸冷却採用の大型PCSは「<strong class='font-semibold'>SAVEEN IM 4000</strong>」。" data-lang-en="Product name: ESS PCS '<strong class='font-semibold'>SAVEEN</strong>'. Large PCS employing immersion cooling is '<strong class='font-semibold'>SAVEEN IM 4000</strong>'.">製品名: ESS用PCS「<strong class='font-semibold'>SAVEEN</strong>」。液浸冷却採用の大型PCSは「<strong class='font-semibold'>SAVEEN IM 4000</strong>」。</p>
                        <p data-lang-ja="実績: 国内外で合計<strong class='font-semibold'>519台</strong>、<strong class='font-semibold'>474MW</strong>出荷 (2024年末時点)。" data-lang-en="Track record: Total of <strong class='font-semibold'>519 units</strong>, <strong class='font-semibold'>474MW</strong> shipped domestically and internationally (as of end 2024).">実績: 国内外で合計<strong class='font-semibold'>519台</strong>、<strong class='font-semibold'>474MW</strong>出荷 (2024年末時点)。</p>
                        <h3 class="sub-section-title" data-lang-ja="SAVEEN IM 4000 仕様" data-lang-en="SAVEEN IM 4000 Specifications"><strong class="font-semibold">SAVEEN IM 4000</strong> 仕様</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mb-2">
                            <li data-lang-ja="構成: <strong class='font-semibold'>4MW</strong>ステーション" data-lang-en="Configuration: <strong class='font-semibold'>4MW</strong> station">構成: <strong class='font-semibold'>4MW</strong>ステーション</li>
                            <li data-lang-ja="最大DC許容電圧: <strong class='font-semibold'>1,500V</strong>" data-lang-en="Max DC allowable voltage: <strong class='font-semibold'>1,500V</strong>">最大DC許容電圧: <strong class='font-semibold'>1,500V</strong></li>
                            <li data-lang-ja="定格電力: <strong class='font-semibold'>4,000kW</strong>" data-lang-en="Rated power: <strong class='font-semibold'>4,000kW</strong>">定格電力: <strong class='font-semibold'>4,000kW</strong></li>
                            <li data-lang-ja="系統電圧: <strong class='font-semibold'>690V</strong>" data-lang-en="Grid voltage: <strong class='font-semibold'>690V</strong>">系統電圧: <strong class='font-semibold'>690V</strong></li>
                            <li data-lang-ja="通信: Modbus RTU/TCP, IEC61850, CAN" data-lang-en="Communication: Modbus RTU/TCP, IEC61850, CAN">通信: Modbus RTU/TCP, IEC61850, CAN</li>
                            <li data-lang-ja="保護レベル: <strong class='font-semibold'>IP65 / NEMA 3R</strong>" data-lang-en="Protection level: <strong class='font-semibold'>IP65 / NEMA 3R</strong>">保護レベル: <strong class='font-semibold'>IP65 / NEMA 3R</strong></li>
                            <li data-lang-ja="運転温度範囲: <strong class='font-semibold'>-20℃ ～ +50℃</strong> (<strong class='font-semibold'>ディレーティングなし</strong>)" data-lang-en="Operating temperature range: <strong class='font-semibold'>-20°C to +50°C</strong> (<strong class='font-semibold'>no derating</strong>)">運転温度範囲: <strong class='font-semibold'>-20℃ ～ +50℃</strong> (<strong class='font-semibold'>ディレーティングなし</strong>)
                                <button class="term-explain-button" data-term-ja="ディレーティング" data-term-en="Derating">✨<span data-lang-key="explain_term_button" data-lang-ja="解説" data-lang-en="Explain">解説</span></button>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <p data-lang-ja="設計: <strong class='font-semibold'>モジュール設計</strong>による容易なメンテナンス性。<strong class='font-semibold'>1+n設計</strong>による高い信頼性。<strong class='font-semibold'>3レベル技術</strong>。外部空気遮断により過酷環境に適応。" data-lang-en="Design: Easy maintenance due to <strong class='font-semibold'>modular design</strong>. High reliability with <strong class='font-semibold'>1+n design</strong>. <strong class='font-semibold'>3-level technology</strong>. Adaptable to harsh environments by blocking external air.">設計: <strong class='font-semibold'>モジュール設計</strong>による容易なメンテナンス性。<strong class='font-semibold'>1+n設計</strong>による高い信頼性。<strong class='font-semibold'>3レベル技術</strong>。外部空気遮断により過酷環境に適応。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                 <div class="mt-4">
                    <button class="accordion-button">
                        <span data-lang-ja="3.3. 液浸冷却のメリット" data-lang-en="3.3. Advantages of Immersion Cooling">3.3. 液浸冷却のメリット</span>
                        <span class="arrow">&#9654;</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content p-4 bg-white border border-t-0 rounded-b-md">
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mb-2">
                            <li data-lang-ja="電子部品の<strong class='font-semibold'>故障原因を削減</strong>（最大78%とされる要因）。" data-lang-en="<strong class='font-semibold'>Reduces causes of electronic component failure</strong> (factors said to be up to 78%).">電子部品の<strong class='font-semibold'>故障原因を削減</strong>（最大78%とされる要因）。</li>
                            <li data-lang-ja="空冷式比で部品損傷や<strong class='font-semibold'>火災リスクを最小限に抑制</strong>。" data-lang-en="<strong class='font-semibold'>Minimizes component damage and fire risk</strong> compared to air-cooled systems.">空冷式比で部品損傷や<strong class='font-semibold'>火災リスクを最小限に抑制</strong>。</li>
                            <li data-lang-ja="オイル封入による<strong class='font-semibold'>IP65以上</strong>の高防塵防水性能（高湿度環境、産業用途で特に有効）。" data-lang-en="<strong class='font-semibold'>High dust/water proofing (IP65+)</strong> due to oil sealing (particularly effective in high-humidity environments and industrial applications).">オイル封入による<strong class='font-semibold'>IP65以上</strong>の高防塵防水性能（高湿度環境、産業用途で特に有効）。</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="conversation-info">
                            <p data-lang-ja="[会話情報] <strong class='font-semibold'>メンテナンス頻度の低減</strong>期待。" data-lang-en="[Conversation Info] Expectation of <strong class='font-semibold'>reduced maintenance frequency</strong>."><strong>[会話情報]</strong> <strong class='font-semibold'>メンテナンス頻度の低減</strong>期待。</p>
                            <p data-lang-ja="[会話情報] <strong class='font-semibold'>CAPEX（設備投資）の削減</strong>期待。" data-lang-en="[Conversation Info] Expectation of <strong class='font-semibold'>CAPEX reduction</strong>."><strong>[会話情報]</strong> <strong class='font-semibold'>CAPEX（設備投資）の削減</strong>期待。</p>
                            <p data-lang-ja="[会話情報] 優れた冷却性能により<strong class='font-semibold'>電力容量が増加</strong>し、<strong class='font-semibold'>コスト競争力が向上</strong>。" data-lang-en="[Conversation Info] <strong class='font-semibold'>Increased power capacity</strong> due to excellent cooling performance, <strong class='font-semibold'>improving cost competitiveness</strong>."><strong>[会話情報]</strong> 優れた冷却性能により<strong class='font-semibold'>電力容量が増加</strong>し、<strong class='font-semibold'>コスト競争力が向上</strong>。</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-1">
                                <li data-lang-ja="<strong class='font-semibold'>50℃までの環境温度で電力ディレーティングなし</strong>運転可能。" data-lang-en="Operation possible <strong class='font-semibold'>without power derating at ambient temperatures up to 50°C</strong>."><strong class='font-semibold'>50℃までの環境温度で電力ディレーティングなし</strong>運転可能。</li>
                                <li data-lang-ja="IGBT定格電力の<strong class='font-semibold'>1.5倍運転</strong>、インダクターの安定した運転が可能。" data-lang-en="Operation at <strong class='font-semibold'>1.5 times IGBT rated power</strong> and stable inductor operation possible.">IGBT定格電力の<strong class='font-semibold'>1.5倍運転</strong>、インダクターの安定した運転が可能。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
